In the Matter of AZIMJON A. Administration for Children's Services, Respondent
v.
ADOLAT K., Appellant, et al., Respondent. 2018-610 Court of Appeals of New York. Decided August 30, 2018

(And Another Proceeding)

***926Motion for leave to appeal dismissed upon the ground that the order sought to be appealed from does not finally determine the proceedings within the meaning of the Constitution.
